		<article>

			<div class="meta">
				

				<div class="details">
					<h1>PHP Form Classes</h1>

					<div class="desc">
						<time datetime="2010-10-05T00:00:00+00:00" pubdate="pubdate">
							October 2010						</time>

						<p>I developed a set of PHP5 classes to enable the rapid production of form-based web applications.</p>

<p><em>Features include&hellip;</em></p>

<ul>
<li>Read/Write database scaffolding</li>
<li>Optional (<em>but sexy</em>) AJAX processing</li>
<li>Step based session forms</li>
<li>Sensible defaults + powerful config</li>
<li>Individual field and global error messages</li>
<li>Payment gateway integration for checkout forms</li>
</ul>

<p>There is a impoverished version of these classes on <a href="https://github.com/clearbar/Form-Builder">Github</a>. I'm working on full featured code, but much is heavily integrated with a private codebase.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				
				
				
				
			</div>

